import React, { useState } from 'react'; import classes from "./PaymentPage.module.css" import Title from '../../Components/Title/Title'; const PaymentPage = () => { const [order, setOrder] = useState(); const { user, address } = useAuth(); return ( <>
<div className={classes.summary}> <div> <h3>Name:</h3> <span>{order.user}</span> </div> <div> <h3>Address:</h3> <span>{order.address}</span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </> ) } export default PaymentPage
